Button\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2534615\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 13, 2022</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zua1665702948382.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zua1665702948382.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zua1665702948382.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zua1665702948382\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Index Management on Microsoft SQL Server\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"zua1665702948382__index_management_on_microsoft_sql_server_158014\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zua1665702948382__p_d52904e1_d52905e1_d52906e1\">The following types of index are created:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zua1665702948382__li_d24836e1_d24837e1_d24838e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zua1665702948382__p_d52907e1_d52908e1_d52909e1\">UNIQUE CLUSTERED—primary keys</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zua1665702948382__li_d24839e1_d24840e1_d24841e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zua1665702948382__p_d52910e1_d52911e1_d52912e1\">UNIQUE NON-CLUSTERED—candidate keys</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zua1665702948382__li_d24842e1_d24843e1_d24844e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zua1665702948382__p_d52913e1_d52914e1_d52915e1\">NON-UNIQUE, NON-CLUSTERED—all others</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zua1665702948382__p_d52916e1_d52917e1_d52918e1\">The index is created when the table is created, either on-the-fly or by running SQL scripts generated by the Create Table facility.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zua1665702948382__p_d52919e1_d52920e1_d52921e1\">The syntax for index names is <var class=\"keyword varname\">TableName</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">I</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var>, where <var class=\"keyword varname\">n</var> is the number of the index. If a table name is too long to allow this, within the 30 character limit, Uniface truncates it accordingly.</p>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534615\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2534615\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Index Management on Microsoft SQL Server Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 13, 2022 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Index Management on Microsoft SQL Server The following types of index are created: UNIQUE CLUSTERED—primary keys UNIQUE NON-CLUSTERED—candidate keys NON-UNIQUE, NON-CLUSTERED—all others The index is created when the table is created, either on-the-fly or by running SQL scripts generated by the Create Table facility. The syntax for index names is TableName I n , where n is the number of the index. If a table name is too long to allow this, within the 30 character limit, Uniface truncates it accordingly. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}